                    <img src="/flags/vietnam.png" class="w-5 h-5"> Vietnam
                </li>
                <li data-value="vn" data-img="/flags/vietnam.png"
                    class="flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 hover:bg-[#3a003c] text-white cursor-pointer">
                    <img src="/flags/vietnam.png" class="w-5 h-5"> Vietnam
                </li>
                <li data-value="vn" data-img="/flags/vietnam.png"
